We will need to tokenize and strip punctuation from the strigs for the Frequency Charts
Additionally with the Neuro Linguistic toolkit we can strip the stopwords
you may have to use nltk.download('punct') in order to use the english
punctuation inthe tokenizer

In [62]:
punc = re.compile('\w+')
Genesis_Frequency = FreqDist([word for word in word_tokenize(Genesis) if word not in stopwords.words() and punc.match(word)])
In [74]:
def Book_Frequency(book):
    punc = re.compile('\w+')
    Book_Frequency = FreqDist([word for word in word_tokenize(book) if word not in stopwords.words() and punc.match(word)])
    return Book_Frequency

Now we can use the Book_Frequency method to Render the rest of the Frequencies

In [75]:
Exodus_Frequency = Book_Frequency(Exodus)
Leviticus_Frequency = Book_Frequency(Leviticus)
Number_Frequency = Book_Frequency(Numbers)
Deuteronomy_Frequency = Book_Frequency(Deuteronomy)
